author: Tony Garcia | agarcia6@mlive.com
title: Meet Grass Lake's straight-A, three-sport athlete Jonathan Lutchka
text: Jonathan Lutchka had no plans to play college sports until earlier this year. Thanks to a standout performance as Grass Lake's quarterback, that became an option after the senior led the Warriors to a nine-win season and a Cascades Conference championship.
